Description:
East Facing Marvel in the heart of Truganina - Very close to three prominent schools & Childcare!!
Only on the rarest occasion does an allotment offering such dramatic dimensions and irresistible potential become available in such a rewarding context as this sought after lifestyle street, here in the heart of Truganina. Boasting a sundrenched frontage and sleek contemporary spaces, this immaculate & sensationally stylish home offers an exceptional lifestyle which is just waiting to be enjoyed.
With close proximity to the popular schools such as Truganina South Primary, Westbourne Grammar School, Al-Taqwa College, Wyndham Village Shopping Centre, Williams Landing & Tarneit Train Stations, Parks, Walking Tracks, Local Community Centre, Shops & Easy Freeway Access, convenience and comfort can't get any better than this!
Walk into this East Facing superb family house in great location and be amazed. This vibrant house is full of energy thanks to its open layout and practical floorplan. The proportions are impressive and the living is immaculate, with a voluminous open plan family/meals area being the perfect accompaniment to an immensely spacious modern kitchen with magnificent island bench, 900 mm appliances, and elegant built in pantry.
This charming home offers 3 spacious bedrooms featuring a very impressive and generous sized master bedroom at the entrance that includes an elegant walk in robe and a stunning ensuite. The bedrooms 2 and 3 comprise of built in robes, and are serviced by a central bathroom.
This welcoming and spacious home offers a very spacious formal lounge and a gorgeous Open plan living area.
To add to the long list of luxuries offered by this splendid family home, centralized ducted heating and split system air con are a couple of features that will assure you of comfort inside, whereas the fabulous outdoor entertainment area has a wide open beautifully landscaped & well-maintained backyard featuring an Alfresco with timber decking.
Offers a generous sized laundry area with linen storage space and side access plus a remote controlled double garage with internal and rear access to suit your needs and add convenience.
This opportunity for a perfect home is not to be missed! End your search for a perfect dream house now!
Contact Raj on 0470 648 329 today to discuss the details!

Superbly located within close proximity to parks, public transport, Ballarat Rd, Western Highway, CS train station, Burnside Hub & only minutes to CS square & town centre.

Description:
ITS A SHAW THING
Built with pride and showcasing a level of craftsmanship that is rarely found and offered, this fully equipped modern family haven delivers everything that a growing family could want and desire in a home. Nestled in the prestigious zone of Kororoit Creek Primary School this rarity is surely not to be missed. The floor-plan has been carefully laid out with a view to modern day functionality, and it offers multiple living zones where every space will serve a purpose to each member of your family.
Property features include:
Master bedroom showcasing a large fitted walk-in wardrobe and ensuite with double vanity and quality fittings
Additional three spacious bedrooms all with built-in wardrobes and ceiling fans
The open plan kitchen is located perfectly to incorporate the meals and family zone with a gas fire place which leads out to a gorgeous alfresco area with ceiling fan, solid timber decking and a Jacuzzi
Kitchen complete with ample cupboard space, caesar stone bench tops, first class stainless steel appliances including 900mm freestanding oven with gas cook top, range hood, dishwasher and double sink
Home theatre or rumpus room
Separate lounge or kids retreat with ceiling fan
Central bathroom with bathtub and quality fittings
Ducted heating, evaporative cooling, floating floorboards, wide hall entrance and high ceilings
Double garage on remote with internal access
Professional landscaped gardens to the front and rear of the property
You will love coming home every day to the unmatched lifestyle features that this property has to offer! For more information or to make an appointment to inspect the property please call Andrew Migliorisi on 0432 526 844 or Stephen Azzopardi on 0402 012 554.

Marvelous Manna

Located within close proximity to Alamanda K-9 College, parkland and wetlands, walking and cycling paths, public transport and all the best that Point Cook has to offer.

A stylish mix of single-level sophistication and spacious indoor/outdoor appeal, this free-flowing 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom entertainer uses space and natural light efficiently in the most requested, sought-after part of Truganina.

Description:
Vacant Land
356 m land with a 12.5 metre frontage.
A recent analysis by leading Australian property advisory firm Jones Lang LaSalle indicated that Wyndham Harbour's rare bayside location, with marina amenities, is likely to significantly appreciate in value following the pattern of waterfront property in neighbouring suburbs.
With the vibrant hub of the Marina Square nearby that will offer a leisure and retail centre, cosmopolitan cafes, restaurants and specialty shops, this allotment represents an unparalleled piece of lifestyle opportunity.
Wyndham Harbour development also features:
Construction of two new beaches
10 hectares of impressive landscaping with purpose-built cycling and walking trails
Marine berths ranging from 10-30 metres
24 hour security and camera surveillance
With the introduction of a ferry the precinct represents an exciting opportunity to enjoy life by the beach at Melbourne's premier bay side community.
Wyndham Harbour is proud to have been awarded the Enviro Development certification; a national sustainability assessment system that provides independent verification of projects sustainability performance, and awards certification to those that achieve exceptional sustainability outcomes which are over and above statutory requirements.

Description:
Irresistible Low Maintenance Living
LJ Hooker Point Cook presents 33 Seagrass Crescent, Point Cook. A home of calm and comfortability, this single-storey residence offers an idyllic low maintenance lifestyle that is hard to resist. Comprising light-filled living zones, four bedrooms, two bathrooms and double car accommodation, this property is well suited to families, professionals and investors. Situated within the picturesque Saratoga Estate and nearby to local shops, schools and public transport, this immaculate home will impress upon inspection.
- With an abundance of natural light, the bright and airy living and dining zones are inviting spaces to rest and unwind, with walls of windows providing views across the gardens. Split system air conditioning ensures year-round comfort, while tiled flooring adds practicality for families.
- Well-appointed and timelessly styled, the kitchen boasts a central island bench and breakfast bar, perfect for casual meals. Overhead cabinetry and a full-sized pantry provide ample storage, while quality appliances include a gas cooktop, under bench oven and dishwasher.
- A total of four spacious bedrooms are offered, each with built-in robes and soft carpets underfoot. The master suite is located at the front of the home, with a walk-in-robe and private ensuite. The remaining bedrooms share access to the modern family bathroom, fitted with a tub and separate toilet.
- The block is flat and fully fenced with low maintenance gardens and a sunny patio, ideal for outdoor dining and entertaining family and friends.
- Additional highlights of this wonderful home include a double remote-control garage with internal access, a separate laundry with storage, ducted heating, split system air conditioning and roller blinds throughout.
Residents will enjoy full access to the Saratoga Estate Recreation Centre, equipped with a state-of-the-art gym, heated indoor swimming pool, basketball half court, covered BBQ area and grassed amphitheater. A choice of quality schools including Featherbook P-9 College and the well-regarded Nino Early Learning Adventures are just a short stroll away, while The Brook Point Cook, Featherbrook Shopping Centre and Featherbrook Reserve are within easy reach. With Melbournes CBD just 25kms away, commuters will benefit from nearby bus and train services, while drivers will enjoy easy access to the Princes Freeway.

This house encompasses open plan living areas and dining area, incorporating a superb MasterChef kitchen fitted with upgraded 900mm appliances, stone bench top and storage including pantry. With added features like ducted heating, evaporative cooling, 2 car garage with remote control, contemporary neutral interiors, spacious laundry, and front landscaping, and alfresco sitting area.
Other inspired features include :-
-Master with a walk-in robe
-Formal lounge
-Remote Controlled double garage
-Fully Landscaped front yard and backyard
-High ceiling, down lights
-Grand alfresco sitting area
Come and view this elevated and elegant family home that's certain to attract an assortment of potential buyers.
Call agent to arrange an inspection as this one won't last long.
